    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone looking for a solid, comfortable car that's ready to go. It\u2019s been well-loved and looked after, so it\u2019s all set for its next adventure with you. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself how great it feels on the road!",
