    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW 540i xDrive is a sophisticated executive sedan that has been meticulously maintained for daily use. The exterior is finished in a striking Bluestone Metallic that still holds a deep, reflective shine. Upon close inspection, you will find minor stone chips on the hood and a small, professionally touched-up scuff on the lower rear bumper, typical for a vehicle of this age. The 19-inch multi-spoke wheels are in great shape, though there is light curb rash on the passenger-side front wheel. Inside, the Mocha Dakota leather remains supple and free of tears; the driver\u2019s seat bolster shows only slight softening from entry and exit. The cabin is smoke-free and all amenities\u2014including the heated seats, sunroof, and the premium Harman Kardon sound system\u2014are in full working order. Under the hood, the 3.0L TwinPower Turbo engine runs flawlessly, backed by a complete service history from authorized centers. The most recent oil service and multi-point inspection were completed just 1,500 miles ago. The tires have approximately 65% tread life remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This car represents a perfect balance for a buyer seeking luxury and performance without the 'new car' price tag.",
      "price": 32500.0,
